                        <decoNote xml:id="b2" type="Cover">Remnants of brown leather cover; <term key="tooling">blind tooled ornament</term> is visible on the front board and on the turn-ins 
                           (at least 9 tools were used: <term key="wavyLine">double sine wave</term>, <term key="tripleStraightLine">triple line fillet</term>, <term key="crissCross">criss-cross</term>,
                           <term key="singleCircle">single circle</term>, <term key="crescent">double crescent</term>, <term key="corniForm">corni-form</term>, <term key="XForm">small x</term>,
                           cross hatching, triple dot fillet.</decoNote>
                           <decoNote xml:id="b3" type="Sewing">Two pairs of sewing stations.</decoNote>
                           <decoNote xml:id="b4" type="SewingStations">4</decoNote>
